-He can see us.

22:04.708 --> 22:05.875
Come on.

22:07.458 --> 22:09.375
-Stop, stop, stop.
-That's a travel.

22:09.458 --> 22:12.250
-You can't do that. That's traveling.
-It's what?

22:12.333 --> 22:15.583
Gianni, you got to keep bouncing it, bro.

22:15.666 --> 22:16.708
Keep bouncing it?

22:16.791 --> 22:17.791
Mm-hmm.

22:18.625 --> 22:19.625
Okay.

22:22.250 --> 22:23.250
Hey, hey, hey.

22:26.458 --> 22:27.541
The basket, man.

22:28.041 --> 22:29.958
-Go put the ball in the basket.
-Bro. Ugo.

22:30.041 --> 22:31.250
Put the ball in the basket.

22:31.333 --> 22:32.375
-Over here.
-Shoot!

22:46.000 --> 22:47.458
Hey, hey, hey! Pass it.

22:54.208 --> 22:55.208
Tag.

22:57.083 --> 22:58.583
Giannis. Thanasis.

22:59.583 --> 23:00.958
Oya, second half now.

23:01.041 --> 23:02.916
You should come down to the gym and play.

23:03.000 --> 23:04.916
Youth club. It's free.

23:05.000 --> 23:06.000
Where?

23:06.083 --> 23:07.083
Filathlitikos.

23:07.833 --> 23:08.833
Okay.

23:27.916 --> 23:30.708
Welcome back to
the top ten African basketball players.

23:30.791 --> 23:34.208
