24:00.541 --> 24:02.833
Fake, baseline and he scores.

24:02.916 --> 24:05.625
Hakeem the Dream, what a move!

24:05.708 --> 24:08.166
-Oya, boys. Time for bed.
-If he was the only player on the court,

24:08.250 --> 24:09.791
