25:40.791 --> 25:43.208
If it's safe, maybe we'll take you.

25:43.291 --> 25:44.416
Maybe?

25:44.500 --> 25:45.791
I just grew.

25:45.875 --> 25:47.791
It'll change to "maybe not"
if you don't go to sleep now.

25:47.875 --> 25:49.375
-I grew more!
-Sleep.

25:50.541 --> 25:52.791
You too. Sleep.

26:00.833 --> 26:04.708
Listen,
Papa always talks about opportunity.

26:05.375 --> 26:06.583
What if this is it?

26:07.750 --> 26:09.208
The boy said it's a big club.

26:10.333 --> 26:13.375
If we're good,
maybe they pick us for their team.

26:13.958 --> 26:15.666
Basketball players can make money.

26:16.625 --> 26:18.208
We can help Mom and Dad.

26:18.708 --> 26:21.166
-You think you're that good already?

26:21.250 --> 26:23.958
If it's to help our family,
I will get that good.

27:03.875 --> 27:06.166
MUNICIPAL GYM OF ZOGRAFOS

27:35.833 --> 27:37.083
Gianni.

28:00.333 --> 28:02.416
No wonder we're in last place.

28:02.500 --> 28:05.625
We're terrible. Completely 100% terrible.

28:11.416 --> 28:12.625
Who are these guys?

28:13.125 --> 28:14.125
You know these guys?

28:15.541 --> 28:16.541
They're tall.

28:25.875 --> 28:28.000
What-- What are you guys doing here?

28:30.166 --> 28:35.166
Uh, we're-- we're here to play basketball.
At the, uh-- the-- the free youth camp.

28:35.791 --> 28:39.041
Yes, we need it to be really, really free.

28:42.208 --> 28:44.208
Do your parents know that you're here?

28:44.708 --> 28:47.083
Uh… Our mom dropped us off.

28:47.166 --> 28:50.291
She'll be back later.
She wanted us to do the-- the free--

28:50.375 --> 28:52.041
The free youth club. Yeah, I heard that.

28:52.125 --> 28:54.875
But we're gonna need her signature
before you can play.

28:54.958 --> 28:57.583
But she doesn't know we're here.

28:57.666 --> 28:59.833
Gianni. Man.

29:02.708 --> 29:04.958
-Where are you guys from?
-Sepolia.

29:08.791 --> 29:09.791
Wait here.

29:11.208 --> 29:13.000
Why did you have to tell him
we're from Sepolia?

29:13.083 --> 29:15.250
