1:28:43.625 --> 1:28:45.291
So out of the 30 teams,

1:28:45.375 --> 1:28:49.916
our best shot is anywhere between the 11th
and the 16th pick.

1:28:50.000 --> 1:28:52.166
That's Philadelphia at 11. Boston, 16.

1:28:52.250 --> 1:28:54.333
Oklahoma, Dallas, Utah, Milwaukee
between them.

1:28:54.416 --> 1:28:57.166
-So any team above 11 and below 16--
-They're saying I'm not good.

1:28:59.416 --> 1:29:02.125
Giannis, don't believe everything you see
on TV, okay?

1:29:02.208 --> 1:29:03.291
What about this?

1:29:04.166 --> 1:29:06.125
