1:34:18.166 --> 1:34:20.625
This isn't just some kid
getting drafted, Kevin.

1:34:21.333 --> 1:34:22.375
I know.

1:34:22.458 --> 1:34:24.583
He might never see his family again.

1:34:39.958 --> 1:34:43.416
