I might not get picked at all?

1:34:43.916 --> 1:34:47.416
Hey, people come here all the time
and don't get picked.

1:34:47.500 --> 1:34:50.458
Dwight Buycks. Diante Garrett.
JaMychal Green.

1:34:51.041 --> 1:34:52.708
They all made it to the NBA.

1:34:54.083 --> 1:34:56.416
It's not where you start.
It's where you finish.

1:35:02.333 --> 1:35:03.541
Excuse me. Sorry, sir.

1:35:03.625 --> 1:35:05.000
Excuse me, please. Thank you.

