1:44:02.041 --> 1:44:03.333
And that'll do it!

1:44:04.166 --> 1:44:07.208
The Milwaukee Bucks
are NBA champions once again!

1:44:07.291 --> 1:44:10.083
Finals MVP,
Giannis Antetokounmpo!

1:44:10.166 --> 1:44:12.541
MVP! MVP!

1:44:12.625 --> 1:44:17.833
MVP! MVP! MVP! MVP!

1:44:17.916 --> 1:44:20.625
MVP! MVP!

1:51:07.000 --> 1:51:09.208
-Let's do it again.
-Whoo!

1:51:09.291 --> 1:51:10.291
Yeah.
